{"4424120": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "不小心被妖狐辣妹包養的那件事", "steam_appid": 4424120, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4424120/extras/41ebaa96746657b752df4c068615afd7.poster.avif?t=1776396637\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4424120/extras/41ebaa96746657b752df4c068615afd7.webm?t=1776396637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4424120/extras/41ebaa96746657b752df4c068615afd7.mp4?t=1776396637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【故事簡介】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在社會與黑心公司的打擊下失去一切，甚至被陷害背上債務、遭黑道抓走準備賣到海外。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就在絕望之際，一名陌生的辣妹突然拿出鉅款將你救下。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >半信半疑之下，你被她哄騙回家。不料一進門，對方嶄露的真實身分，竟是回眸一笑百媚生的三尾妖狐!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一無所有的你，就此被妖狐辣妹收養。在與她共度臉紅心跳的同居生活中，你的人生究竟會徹底墜落，還是因這場奇異邂逅迎來新的轉機？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >〈不小心被妖狐辣妹包養的那件事〉就此展開！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4424120/extras/a63325efbd9d99385bbd803fb91ac8f0.avif?t=1776396637\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4424120/extras_big/a63325efbd9d99385bbd803fb91ac8f0.webp?t=1776396637 width=1560 height=1160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【遊戲內容】</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>高自由度的Live2D</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲主線內容使用Live2D製作，除了主線的故事以外，玩家將於互動介面中可依序解鎖手、舌頭、肉棒，以及道具與妖狐進行深入交流。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autopla